<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q49_v5" title="Q49_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un plano cuadriculado, un explorador parte desde un campamento ubicado en las coordenadas 
      <m:math>
        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
        <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        <m:mo>,</m:mo>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Luego realiza los siguientes desplazamientos:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>6 unidades al oeste</li>
      <li>5 unidades al norte</li>
      <li>2 unidades al este</li>
      <li>7 unidades al sur</li>
      <li>4 unidades al este</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      ¿Cuáles son las coordenadas finales del explorador en el plano?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>15</m:mn>
          <m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al sumar los desplazamientos horizontales, la coordenada x queda en 3 − 6 + 2 + 4 = 3, no en 15. Verticalmente, la coordenada y sí queda en −2 + 5 − 7 = −4. Por lo tanto, la posición final es (3, −4), no (15, −4).</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Horizontalmente: 3 − 6 = −3, luego −3 + 2 = −1 y finalmente −1 + 4 = 3. Verticalmente: −2 + 5 = 3 y luego 3 − 7 = −4. Entonces la posición final del explorador es (3, −4).</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          <m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Horizontalmente, la coordenada x final es 3 − 6 + 2 + 4 = 3, no 0. Además, verticalmente la coordenada y final es −2 + 5 − 7 = −4, no −2. Por lo tanto, (0, −2) no corresponde a la posición final.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>,</m:mo>
          <m:mn>10</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La coordenada x final sí resulta 3, porque 3 − 6 + 2 + 4 = 3. Pero la coordenada y final es −2 + 5 − 7 = −4, no 10. Por eso la posición final no es (3, 10), sino (3, −4).</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar el punto de partida</strong></p>
            <p>El explorador parte en:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esto significa que inicialmente <strong>x = 3</strong> e <strong>y = −2</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Aplicar los desplazamientos horizontales</strong></p>
            <p>Ir al oeste disminuye la coordenada <strong>x</strong> e ir al este aumenta la coordenada <strong>x</strong>.</p>
            <p>Partimos con:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Luego:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La coordenada final en el eje horizontal es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Aplicar los desplazamientos verticales</strong></p>
            <p>Ir al norte aumenta la coordenada <strong>y</strong> e ir al sur disminuye la coordenada <strong>y</strong>.</p>
            <p>Partimos con:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Luego:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La coordenada final en el eje vertical es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>y</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Escribir la coordenada final</strong></p>
            <p>Como la coordenada horizontal final es 3 y la vertical final es −4, la posición final del explorador es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>